logs/*
!logs/README.md
*.log
*.smcl
*.tmp
*.temp
~$*
.~lock.*

# Stata, editor, and backup artifacts
*.stswp
*.bak
*.swp
*.swo

# Dropbox conflicts and operating-system files
*conflicted copy*
*Conflicted copy*
